    <Label name="lblWarning" id="d82803fb-3a88-4fc8-acdc-fe22ec830254">
        <caption>When Excel is open it is interacting with the Wizard. At the end of the definition process, pressing the Finish button will save the definition and close Excel automatically. Similarly if you Cancel or close a Wizard form, this will also automatically close Excel. If you close Excel yourself you will lose any updates you may have made to the workbook.</caption>
